As Vulois flys overhead, he detects signals close to him. It seems 
that Arrow, Scamrock and Stronghold have been thrown out of the 
people's group. Vulois contacts them.

"Hey boys, if you want to get back at Stranato, meet me on top of the 
huge mountain the plains in 5 mega-cycles. And be ready for a life-
changer."

He continues to fly off.
